We use your Personal Information only for providing and improving the App. By using the App, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.
Information Collection and Use
When using our App, we may ask you to provide us your personal information that can be used to contact and identify you. The information may include, but are not limited to, your name and email.
Communications
We may use your Personal Information to contact you with newsletters, user research, marketing or promotional materials and other information.
Third party services
We may use third party services such as Google Analytics for Firebase that collect, monitor, and analyse user behaviour towards our App. We also partner with third party ads provider to supply ads for free version of our App.
Security
We value your privacy and our privacy policy ensures that your personal detail will only be used for specific purpose for which is was collected. ¬†We also give users a choice to decide whether they want their data removed from lists used for our marketing campaigns or not.
Privacy Policy Change
With respect to any changes in this Privacy Policy, we will update or change at any time. You should check this page periodically to acknowledge the updated privacy policy.
Data Deletion Policy
1. Learn Quran provides users with full control over their data, including what data is retained and what data is deleted.
2. End users can request all or part of their data to be deleted by sending an email to
contact@learn-quran.co
. Once the request is approved by their company, Learn Quran will delete their data.
Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to reach us at
contact@learn-quran.co
